WEBVTT

00:01.168 --> 00:03.291
Carroll was convicted in 2004

00:03.420 --> 00:05.806
for the murders
of 14 young women.

00:05.950 --> 00:07.341
We need you in Virginia, Ryan.

00:07.471 --> 00:08.685
I'm not an agent anymore.

00:08.794 --> 00:11.160
You caught Carroll.
No one knows him like you do.

00:11.274 --> 00:12.876
So what's my sequel about, Joe?

00:12.991 --> 00:14.969
We're gonna
write this together, Ryan...

00:15.072 --> 00:16.268
Aah!

00:16.717 --> 00:19.265
Even though you
slept with my wife.

00:19.394 --> 00:22.762
I have so many surprises
waiting for you.

00:23.511 --> 00:25.198
Cults, my specialty.

00:25.296 --> 00:27.483
Gay neighbors, the nanny,

00:27.577 --> 00:29.802
how do they figure
into your new plot?

00:29.976 --> 00:31.591
Why is my dad such a bad man?

00:31.708 --> 00:33.656
Maybe he's not so bad.

00:37.579 --> 00:38.630
And where are you going, huh?

00:38.739 --> 00:39.894
You're a liar.

00:41.366 --> 00:42.608
What the hell?

00:42.724 --> 00:44.293
Hey, guys.
This is Megan.

00:44.419 --> 00:45.871
I've never killed
anything before.

00:45.993 --> 00:47.500
We're just getting started.

00:47.586 --> 00:48.860
They're teaching him.

00:49.714 --> 00:51.638
Why did your husband
try to kill you?

00:52.086 --> 00:57.024
Rick can be scary
when he wants to be.

00:57.128 --> 00:58.223
So who has Joey?

00:58.350 --> 00:59.320
I don't know where the kid is.

00:59.429 --> 01:00.437
Does Rick know where Joey is?

01:00.543 --> 01:02.199
I don't know,
but his wife does.

01:02.338 --> 01:03.601
- What?
- Maggie.

01:03.709 --> 01:05.470
Maggie Kester is one of them.

